title: What spending can tell us about the health of a presidential campaign
text: Thursday is the deadline for presidential campaigns to submit their third quarter fundraising reports to the Federal Election Commission. Many campaigns -- confident in their numbers or hoping to inoculate the response to bad ones -- have already released top-line details.
